About benchmark. Tested it on CPU Intel(R) Core(TM) i7-4930K CPU @ 3.40GHz with following script
https://pastebin.com/RvVw52YX

Before testing i modified code so it used only single thread for this operation (since previous version also was single-threaded).

Program output before these changes:

  Average resample time 563.567590714 ms, max time 579.554796219 ms

After:

  Average resample time 83.5015463829 ms, max time 96.137046814 ms

body:
About benchmark. Tested it on CPU Intel(R) Core(TM) i7-4930K CPU @ 3.40GHz with following script 
https://pastebin.com/RvVw52YX

Before testing i modified code so it used only single thread for this operation (since previous version also was single-threaded). 

Program output before these changes:
```
  Average resample time 563.567590714 ms, max time 579.554796219 ms
```
After:
```
  Average resample time 83.5015463829 ms, max time 96.137046814 ms
```
